STATE of New Jersey, Plaintiff-Respondent,
v.
Jamel LEWIS, Defendant-Petitioner. C-874 September Term 2018
082193 Supreme Court of New Jersey. May 14, 2019

ORDER

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-003264-17 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
